    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "马尔科夫模型 (Markov Model)"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                54,
                229,
                447,
                283
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "一最早由AndreiA.Markov，（切比雪夫Chebyshev的一个学生）于1913年提出，它的最原始目的是为了语言上的应用"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                89,
                290,
                940,
                383
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "● 隐马尔科夫模型(Hidden Markov Model，HMM)"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                54,
                388,
                633,
                442
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "－其数学思想是由Baum等人於1966~1970提出"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                88,
                450,
                577,
                496
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "一从某种意义上讲，HMM本身是一个马尔科夫过程的概率函数"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                88,
                501,
                764,
                550
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "在20世纪70年代被CMU的Baker以及IBM的Jelinek等人应用在了语音处理上"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                88,
                555,
                877,
                603
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "之后被广泛应用在了汉语自动分词、词性标注、统计机器翻译等很多方面"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                88,
                609,
                920,
                659
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_header",
            "content": {
                "page_header_content": [
